协议对比

| 特性       | Chat Completion                  | Responses API       | Anthropic Messages  | Vertex AI                          |
| ---------- | -------------------------------- | ------------------- | ------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| 参数名     | `reasoningeffort` / `reasoning` | `reasoning`         | `thinking`          | `thinkingconfig`                  |
